## Install with CLI
::hr-underline
::

This will install the item in the path defined by your `components.json` file, thanks to shadcn-vue.

:::code-group{.w-full}
  ```bash [yarn]
  yarn add @nuxt/ui
  ```
  
  ```bash [npm]
  npm install @nuxt/ui
  ```

  ```bash [pnpm]
  pnpm add @nuxt/ui
  ```
  
  ```bash [bun]
  bun add @nuxt/ui
  ```
:::



